          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659890686631-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy cumin lamb</strong> with the <strong>cooked rice</strong> and <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>smashed cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>reserved pickling liquid</strong> over the cooked rice</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
